eu.mapperproject.jmml.topology.algorithms
Class TaskGraphState

java.lang.Object
  eu.mapperproject.jmml.topology.algorithms.TaskGraphState
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Iterable<ProcessIteration>
public class TaskGraphState
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Iterable<ProcessIteration>

Keeps track of the current state in a task graph. This state involves having active processiterations that can spawn new processiterations and snoozing processiterations which have not received all data necessary to do their computation.

Author:
Joris Borgdorff
